attr.title: The Sword Witch's Apprentice
attr.desc: A brief sword-fighting adventure controlled entirely with the directional inputs. It offers about ten minutes of fast, focused action as you live the life of the Sword Witch's apprentice.
attr.inst: Download the game free at itch.io (https://tinycactus.itch.io/swordwitchsapprentice) and place the game files in theswordwitchsapprentice/gamedata.
attr.inst_md: Download the game free at [itch.io](https://tinycactus.itch.io/swordwitchsapprentice) and place the game files in `theswordwitchsapprentice/gamedata`.
